<br>
Runes still to find and check: Substance, Nagafen, Periphery, Neglect, Opression, Velious, Dismemberment, Regeneration. I am also confused over the Fulguration rune, Mythiran tower (mythiran.allakhazam.com) says there are (azia) and (beza) versions used for wizard research, but I only found a Fulguration rune without those endings, did not yield a valid combination either.<br>
<br>
