I found the two different versions of the Fulguration rune, thanks for the tip...btw. they both identify as &quot;Rune of Fulguration&quot;, and sell for the same money. Only found them because they were next to each other on a vendor <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
