Now after this brute force approach, I have a couple of questions:<br>
<br>
1) Can we be sure that only our research words are to be included into the tests, and not also the research components? I mean there are VASTLY more enc and necro words than magician words.<br>
<br>
2) Why is this quest seemingly centered about wizard runes? Are they anything special? <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
